desc.en: The city is located on a peninsula in the northeastern part of a fictional country. It is the capital of the country. The urban rail transit system consists of two parts:Sopourin Metro and Sopourin Suburban Railway.
desc.zh: 位于一个架空的国家的东北部的半岛上的城市。国家的首都。轨道交通系统由地铁和市郊铁路两部分组成。

reference: 爱发电,Sat Jun 28 2025 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)
